{"tid":1421570,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳皓桓質疑荃灣斬人漢未有被捕  警方：2傷者稱毋須協助","createTime":"2019-08-06T08:24:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T08:27:38.000Z","uid":224066,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"03df82e573fbd7ea238c85f7b5e9bb626be8f10a","tid":1421570,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:24:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/nXyE46dO_nfLyO54veu7aQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20190806a111706.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FnXyE46dO_nfLyO54veu7aQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20190806a111706.jpg&h=42fa1fd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網上流傳多張圖片及片段，指昨日晚上荃灣有人持刀斬人。民陣副召集人陳皓桓出席商台節目時表示，事發時目睹在荃灣眾安街附近，有4、40名白衣人手持刀或棍，追趕一名記者，他跟上前時，發現一名年約20歲的男子被白衣人捉住及斬傷，腳部傷口深見骨。<br />\n<br />\n陳皓桓指，他昨晚與同行的示威者見狀，立即上前協助，制伏2名施襲者，涉事的其他人紛紛逃去。他又指，警方稍後到場，但沒有拘捕被制伏施襲者，反而試圖驅散示威者。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，昨晚11時接報，在眾安街55號對開有多人打鬥，警員到場發現2名傷者，他們被送往仁濟醫院救治。<span style=\"color: red;\">警方指，二人聲稱毋須警方協助，警方在行動中另拘捕一名20歲男子，涉嫌刑事毀壞一部警車。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YQ9MLv4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYQ9MLv4.jpg&h=9a1b367a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"751d2ea6f45bacb8ba8e08a4e60bf40351f2cfa6","tid":1421570,"uid":29381,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:25:03.000Z","msg":"斬人唔係刑事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb70a7ccecd7991f1465d780d87b0d9ee35126ac","tid":1421570,"uid":80624,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T08:11:24.000Z","msg":"刑事案<br />\n有得事主話唔追究就唔做？"},{"pid":"8a4457509bf836cf088736bda3d2744389cfe42e","tid":1421570,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T08:13:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88001d63874d9be244592a99500a2596b9d20bdb","tid":1421570,"uid":34869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T08:15:21.000Z","msg":"斬到咁都唔跟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黑警真係short左"},{"pid":"ded2eb32eddf43493a33125e2ff24d8fe05948d7","tid":1421570,"uid":133501,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T08:16:23.000Z","msg":"香港法治已死，正式進入人治"},{"pid":"8268272f2c464331b4e74e65c412597d8d209d85","tid":1421570,"uid":237517,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T08:17:20.000Z","msg":"刑事 關傷者追唔追究咩事?"},{"pid":"80a26c871ff37d0ce97a634337ffd3f38831846b","tid":1421570,"uid":264301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T08:18:16.000Z","msg":"刑事係警察同律政司要做嘢，你地唔做嘢我都要罷納稅"},{"pid":"b1974b2535b428bcf09b48a67e9ae853881c3ed9","tid":1421570,"uid":16846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T08:21:25.000Z","msg":"香港法治<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a4f03f8ff62732d72f5a5a6651d3c1662b7161c","tid":1421570,"uid":81680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T08:27:38.000Z","msg":"Figo Chan講野信得過？出賣示威者佢就叻"}]}